<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7839eeca-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s543g"><num value="543g">§ 543g.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In addition to other amounts available for such purposes, effective <date date="1985-10-01">October 1, 1985</date>, there are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the purposes of sections 543 to 543h of this title.</p>
